---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="How It Works | Dumpster Machine">
	<main>
		<!-- Header -->
		<section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-20 border-b-8 border-green-600">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
				<h1 class="text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-6">How It Works</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-slate-300 font-medium">Four simple steps to a cleaner project. No headaches, no hidden fees, and you don't even need to be home.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Steps Section -->
		<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-16">
				
				<!-- Step 1 -->
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8 bg-white p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(22,163,74,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
					<div class="w-20 h-20 shrink-0 bg-slate-900 text-green-500 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">1</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-3 text-slate-900">Pick Your Size & Price</h3>
						<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							Landfills charge us by the weight. That’s just physics, and we can't change it. Every dumpster comes with a generous weight allowance and a generous number of days included in the price. We put those numbers in bold print. If your project is heavy and you go over that limit, there is an overage fee—but we tell you exactly what that per 1,000 lb fee is before you ever book. No hidden 'processing' fees. You just pay for the extra weight. That's it.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Step 2 -->
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8 bg-white p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(22,163,74,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
					<div class="w-20 h-20 shrink-0 bg-slate-900 text-green-500 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">2</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-3 text-slate-900">We Drop It Off</h3>
						<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							You don't need to be home. Just tell us where to put it (plywood recommended) and ensure 30-60 feet of clear space for our massive trucks to maneuver. Keeping the area unblocked saves you from a wasted trip fee. 
							<br><br><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> We can't guarantee exact times due to traffic, landfills, and DOT rules stopping drivers from taking calls. To avoid stress, schedule your delivery for the day before your project starts—we give you that extra day for FREE.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Step 3 -->
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8 bg-white p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(22,163,74,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
					<div class="w-20 h-20 shrink-0 bg-slate-900 text-green-500 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">3</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-3 text-slate-900">Load It Up (Stay Under The Line)</h3>
						<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							Fill the box, but nothing can stick over the fill line. Customers often think it’s OK because a tarp goes over the top, but those tarps cost thousands of dollars and debris sticking over the top rips them. It’s also a hazard for other drivers and against DOT regulations.
							<br><br>As for debris, use common sense. Keep hazardous items out (tires, wet paint, batteries—if you can't eat or drink it, and it's poisonous, keep it out). If we can't take it, usually no one can because we all take it to the same landfill.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Step 4 -->
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8 bg-white p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(22,163,74,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
					<div class="w-20 h-20 shrink-0 bg-slate-900 text-green-500 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">4</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-3 text-slate-900">Call Us When You're Done</h3>
						<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							We operate on a call-in basis. We don't schedule the pickup until you tell us you're ready. If your project runs long, it's just a small, transparent daily fee. Work at your own pace, and call us when you're done. We'll send our vetted local crew to haul it away. Just like delivery, ensure that same 30-60 feet of clearance is totally unobstructed so our truck can safely retrieve the box without a wasted trip fee!
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>
			
			<div class="text-center mt-20">
				<a href="/quote" class="bg-green-600 text-slate-900 font-black text-2xl px-12 py-6 rounded-sm shadow-[6px_6px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:translate-x-[4px] transition-all uppercase tracking-wider inline-block">
					Find My City & Price
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
